<h3 id="q%3A-how-to-create-a-new-project-within-the-solution%3F" tabindex="-1">Q: How to create a new project within the solution? <a class="direct-link" href="#q%3A-how-to-create-a-new-project-within-the-solution%3F">ðŸ”—</a></h3>
<p>A1: Solution Explorer â†’ Right click on Solution â†’ Add â†’ New project or Existing Project</p>
<p>A2: Top Menu â†’ File â†’ Add â†’ New project or Existing Project</p>
<h3 id="q%3A-how-to-change-the-.net-version%3F" tabindex="-1">Q: How to change the .NET version? <a class="direct-link" href="#q%3A-how-to-change-the-.net-version%3F">ðŸ”—</a></h3>
<p>A1: Double click on the project file to open the project as XML and edit the <code>&lt;TargetFramework&gt;net5.0&lt;/TargetFramework&gt;</code> tag.</p>
<p>A2: Solution Explorer â†’ Right Click on the Project â†’ Click Properties â†’ Click Application â†’ Change Target Framework</p>
